{"tid":1972084,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇高手可以教小妹捉將棋","createTime":"2020-04-14T10:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T00:54:06.000Z","uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5a00a508a8a32645ea05e98feaf4dc45624161d9","tid":1972084,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:09:47.000Z","msg":"除咗玩下詰仲有咩做<br />\n得閒睇下棋但完全睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係識幾個基本戰術<br />\n想去到睇職業棋睇得明個level<br />\n當多種娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ceb13f4b364eb1d36bd44c6acf45f63a782529","tid":1972084,"uid":168730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"搵棋靈王教你"},{"pid":"52ce780be81492db280ad2c40da6abe1d9da08f5","tid":1972084,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3ceb13f4b364eb1d36bd44c6acf45f63a782529","tid":1972084,"uid":168730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"搵棋靈王教你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"佢係圍棋<br />\n小妹跟開龍王搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00cb8b3d6ac27c5f62d7d68ccdaf69988a44b59","tid":1972084,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"每步行之前要睇下對方會唔會食你d棋，同埋要諗埋之後嗰幾步"},{"pid":"f4c9d5e479ec1a91f6e442d150e824482177aa5d","tid":1972084,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00cb8b3d6ac27c5f62d7d68ccdaf69988a44b59","tid":1972084,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"每步行之前要睇下對方會唔會食你d棋，同埋要諗埋之後嗰幾步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:30:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AGOPVqxIoBc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAGOPVqxIoBc&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=80ec9d51\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AGOPVqxIoBc</a><br />\n睇呢啲解說先稍微有